Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.85,0:22:34.99,ED II Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur6}imada kono te ni nokoru kakera datte
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.53,0:22:44.62,ED II Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur6}anata no mono
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.62,0:22:51.17,ED II Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur6}nanimokamo nakushitemo
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.50,0:22:55.34,ED II Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur6}sasageru mono ga aru no
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.13,0:23:03.31,ED II Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur6}mirai datte inochi de sae
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.73,0:23:14.07,ED II Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur6}yaketsukita kanjou mo fumou na inori mo
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.07,0:23:19.78,ED II Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur6}sugaru buzama mo mitsugu oroka mo
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.78,0:23:25.49,ED II Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur6}yanda koe mo kegareta ryoote mo
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.25,0:23:35.59,ED II Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur6}kizu de fusagareta kokoro mo
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.92,0:22:17.43,ED II Kanji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur6}破滅さえ厭わないで
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.85,0:22:34.99,ED II Kanji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur6}未だこの手に残る欠片だって
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.53,0:22:44.62,ED II Kanji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur6}あなたのもの
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.62,0:22:51.17,ED II Kanji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur6}何もかも失くしても
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.50,0:22:55.34,ED II Kanji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur6}捧げるものがあるの
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.13,0:23:03.31,ED II Kanji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur6}未来だって　命でさえ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.73,0:23:14.07,ED II Kanji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur6}焼け尽きた感情も　不毛な祈りも
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.07,0:23:19.78,ED II Kanji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur6}縋る無様も　見継ぐ愚かも
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.78,0:23:25.49,ED II Kanji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur6}病んだ声も　汚れた両手
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.25,0:23:35.59,ED II Kanji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur6}傷で塞がれた心も
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.92,0:22:17.43,ED II BR,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur6}Não odeie a destruição também.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.85,0:22:34.99,ED II BR,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur6}Ei, até os pedaços que restam nestas mãos
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.53,0:22:44.62,ED II BR,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur6}pertencem a você.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.62,0:22:51.17,ED II BR,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur6}Mesmo que eu perca tudo,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.50,0:22:55.34,ED II BR,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur6}ainda tenho algo a oferecer.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.13,0:23:03.31,ED II BR,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur6}Meu futuro, minha vida...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.73,0:23:14.07,ED II BR,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur6}Minhas emoções fervorosas, minhas orações infrutíferas,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.07,0:23:19.78,ED II BR,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur6}a feiura a qual me agarro, a tolice que forneço,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.78,0:23:25.49,ED II BR,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur6}minha voz insatisfeita, minhas mãos sujas,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.25,0:23:35.59,ED II BR,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur6}e meu coração, aberto pelas cicatrizes.
